ActAn Act to implement conventions between Canada and New Zealand and Canada and Australia for the avoidance of double taxation with respect to income tax
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue giving notice that the Protocol amending the Convention between Canada and AUSTRALIA for the avoidance of double taxation and the prevention of fiscal evasion with respect to taxes on income, signed at Canberra on January 23, 2002, CAME INTO FORCE on December 18, 2002.
